# Portfolio â€” Architecture Memory

Personal portfolio site for Rene Krajnc (frontend developer). Live at `https://www.renekrajnc.com`.

## Tech stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 16 with the **Pages Router** (`src/pages`), React 19, TypeScript strict mode.
- **Styling**: SCSS Modules + Material UI 7 (`@mui/material`, `@mui/icons-material`, `@emotion/*`). Some FontAwesome icons (`@fortawesome/*`).
- **i18n**: `next-i18next` (locales `en`, `sl`, `de`; default `en`). Per-page `getStaticProps` calls `serverSideTranslations(locale, ['common'])`.
- **Forms**: `react-hook-form`. Email via **Resend** + **React Email** templates.
- **Security**: Google reCAPTCHA v3 (server-side verify). CSP/HSTS/etc set in `next.config.ts`.
- **Hosting**: Vercel.

## Path aliases & tooling

- TS path alias: `@/*` â†’ `src/*`.
- ESLint flat config (`eslint.config.mjs`) with `simple-import-sort` + `unused-imports`.
- Prettier: single quotes, semis, 100 width, trailing commas, `endOfLine: auto`. Import order: `^[a-z]`, `^@/`, `^../`, `^./`.
- Scripts: `npm run dev` (webpack), `build`, `start`, `lint`, `tsc`, `format`.

